{"id":"1KpFw59fMA59eEgz","meta":{"instanceId":"ec3f0bbe56f36dfaebd15670149e0f2435ef811a841a277e682bc391adfda47a"},"name":"Grade system prompt with LLM judge","tags":[],"nodes":[{"id":"ad5d70f6-1188-474c-a76d-6fdf93d4b96a","name":"Sticky Note","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-64,32],"parameters":{"width":480,"height":768,"content":"## Grade system prompt with LLM judge\n\n### How it works\n\nThis workflow manually runs a prompt-grading process that reads prompt entries from Google Sheets, keeps the latest row, and attaches a sample task. It sends the prompt and task to a candidate AI agent, then passes the generated answer to a separate LLM judge that returns a structured grade. Finally, it writes the grade back to the Google Sheet.\n\n### Setup steps\n\n- Configure Google Sheets credentials for both the read and write sheet nodes.\n- Set the source spreadsheet, sheet/range, and destination update target in the Google Sheets nodes.\n- Configure Google Gemini credentials for the candidate model and grader model subnodes.\n- Verify the prompt sheet contains the expected prompt fields and that the grade output schema matches the columns being written back.\n\n### Customization\n\nAdjust the sample task in the Set Sample Task node, change the candidate or grader Gemini models, or modify the structured grade schema to capture different evaluation criteria."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"92326cfe-f6d3-4e1a-aa91-7a88237e3e76","name":"Sticky Note1","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[496,32],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":880,"height":352,"content":"## Load latest prompt\n\nStarts the workflow manually, reads prompt rows from Google Sheets, keeps only the most recent row, and adds the sample task that will be used for evaluation."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"0a635feb-c323-4994-92b8-ea46fac7acdf","name":"Sticky Note2","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1392,32],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":352,"height":544,"content":"## Run candidate agent\n\nGenerates the candidate response using the selected Gemini chat model and the prepared prompt/task input."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"9f23e384-5412-4729-abed-03ca017bb05d","name":"Sticky Note3","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[1776,32],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":464,"height":736,"content":"## Judge candidate response\n\nUses a separate Gemini-powered grading agent to evaluate the candidate output and format the result according to the structured grade schema."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"31c23490-d89c-472b-b8bc-5966e0d7fb3b","name":"Sticky Note4","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[2272,32],"parameters":{"color":7,"width":272,"height":336,"content":"## Write grade result\n\nStores the structured grading result back into Google Sheets for tracking and review."},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"839e9e13-595b-4ec7-b40e-9a9418ad4b33","name":"Start Grading Process","type":"n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger","position":[544,208],"parameters":{},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"1f684b9a-b81e-42c8-84ed-d0d62fa07915","name":"Read Prompts from Sheets","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","position":[768,208],"parameters":{"options":{},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gid=0","cachedResultUrl":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1EJRQb8nTNGR7TzxxuYhWP-_Xv3EGJxwf5twprqjPIvI/edit#gid=0","cachedResultName":"Sheet1"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"1EJRQb8nTNGR7TzxxuYhWP-_Xv3EGJxwf5twprqjPIvI","cachedResultUrl":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1EJRQb8nTNGR7TzxxuYhWP-_Xv3EGJxwf5twprqjPIvI/edit?usp=drivesdk","cachedResultName":"System Prompt Grader"}},"typeVersion":4.7},{"id":"e0465e5c-e51f-4ee9-9fc8-39b706e0de33","name":"Limit to Last 10 Prompts","type":"n8n-nodes-base.limit","position":[992,208],"parameters":{"keep":"lastItems"},"typeVersion":1},{"id":"5203a52a-34de-42ae-938a-743eae5c746a","name":"Set Sample Grading Task","type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","position":[1216,208],"parameters":{"options":{},"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"sample-task-1","name":"sampleTask","type":"string","value":"I ordered a blue jacket last week but received a red one. I'm really frustrated — can you help?"}]},"includeOtherFields":true},"typeVersion":3.4},{"id":"54eee5b2-6b37-475d-8b0b-b5f25032c9d5","name":"Candidate Evaluation Agent","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent","position":[1440,208],"parameters":{"text":"={{ $('Set Sample Grading Task').item.json.sampleTask }}","options":{"systemMessage":"={{ $('Set Sample Grading Task').item.json.prompt }}","enableStreaming":false},"promptType":"define"},"typeVersion":3.1},{"id":"eb1840bf-fbf9-4704-8545-ed6463ed4f5a","name":"Gemini Candidate Model","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGoogleGemini","position":[1520,432],"parameters":{"options":{},"modelName":"models/gemini-2.5-flash"},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"37031639-fdde-476c-9af6-4922e0012b02","name":"Grade Evaluation Agent","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent","position":[1856,208],"parameters":{"text":"=SYSTEM PROMPT UNDER TEST:\n{{ $('Set Sample Grading Task').item.json.prompt }}\n\nUSER TASK GIVEN TO THE AGENT:\n{{ $('Set Sample Grading Task').item.json.sampleTask }}\n\nAGENT RESPONSE TO EVALUATE:\n{{ $json.output }}","options":{"systemMessage":"You are a strict evaluator of system prompts for AI agents. You will be given: (1) the SYSTEM PROMPT that was under test, (2) the USER TASK it was applied to, and (3) the RESPONSE an AI agent produced using that system prompt. Judge how well the SYSTEM PROMPT did its job: did it lead to a helpful, on-persona, complete, and appropriate response to the task? Grade from 1 (poor) to 10 (excellent). Be critical and consistent. In \"reason\", give 1-3 sentences citing specific strengths or weaknesses of the PROMPT (missing instructions, unclear persona, no next-step guidance, etc.), not only the response.","enableStreaming":false},"promptType":"define","hasOutputParser":true},"typeVersion":3.1},{"id":"f2a17501-6471-40e9-ae20-c685182db0f9","name":"Gemini Grader Model","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGoogleGemini","position":[1856,432],"parameters":{"options":{"temperature":0.2},"modelName":"models/gemini-2.5-flash"},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"e728717d-f94d-4420-9fe2-a505e0dc6148","name":"Parse Grade Schema","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.outputParserStructured","position":[1984,432],"parameters":{"autoFix":true,"schemaType":"manual","inputSchema":"{\"type\":\"object\",\"properties\":{\"grade\":{\"type\":\"integer\",\"minimum\":1,\"maximum\":10},\"reason\":{\"type\":\"string\"}},\"required\":[\"grade\",\"reason\"],\"additionalProperties\":false}"},"typeVersion":1.3},{"id":"35080fdf-6f2b-4722-8312-496b2472bedb","name":"Gemini Parser Fixer Model","type":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatGoogleGemini","position":[2000,640],"parameters":{"options":{},"modelName":"models/gemini-2.5-flash"},"typeVersion":1.1},{"id":"60fa8ced-d8b3-41f6-afd8-a9fed057a11f","name":"Update Grade in Sheets","type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","position":[2352,208],"parameters":{"columns":{"value":{"grade":"={{ $json.output.grade }}","reason":"={{ $json.output.reason }}","row_number":"={{ $('Read Prompts from Sheets').item.json.row_number }}"},"schema":[{"id":"prompt","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"prompt","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"grade","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"grade","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"reason","type":"string","display":true,"required":false,"displayName":"reason","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true},{"id":"row_number","type":"number","display":true,"removed":false,"readOnly":true,"required":false,"displayName":"row_number","defaultMatch":false,"canBeUsedToMatch":true}],"mappingMode":"defineBelow","matchingColumns":["row_number"],"attemptToConvertTypes":false,"convertFieldsToString":false},"options":{},"operation":"update","sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"gid=0","cachedResultUrl":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1EJRQb8nTNGR7TzxxuYhWP-_Xv3EGJxwf5twprqjPIvI/edit#gid=0","cachedResultName":"Sheet1"},"documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"1EJRQb8nTNGR7TzxxuYhWP-_Xv3EGJxwf5twprqjPIvI","cachedResultUrl":"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1EJRQb8nTNGR7TzxxuYhWP-_Xv3EGJxwf5twprqjPIvI/edit?usp=drivesdk","cachedResultName":"System Prompt Grader"}},"typeVersion":4.7},{"id":"d0bb85b0-bb10-4157-b3ee-0149b62e1063","name":"Sticky Note5","type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","position":[-64,816],"parameters":{"color":"#BAD9FE","width":480,"height":224,"content":"## Get help with the setup and more workflows\n\n vylos-ai.com/   \n\n## Video on prompt chaining\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YZDnJ6bYVdA"},"typeVersion":1}],"active":false,"pinData":{},"settings":{"binaryMode":"separate","executionOrder":"v1"},"versionId":"5cc7d82e-fabe-405d-bcce-c3c78716225e","nodeGroups":[],"connections":{"Parse Grade Schema":{"ai_outputParser":[[{"node":"Grade Evaluation Agent","type":"ai_outputParser","index":0}]]},"Gemini Grader Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Grade Evaluation Agent","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Start Grading Process":{"main":[[{"node":"Read Prompts from Sheets","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Gemini Candidate Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Candidate Evaluation Agent","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Grade Evaluation Agent":{"main":[[{"node":"Update Grade in Sheets","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Set Sample Grading Task":{"main":[[{"node":"Candidate Evaluation Agent","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Limit to Last 10 Prompts":{"main":[[{"node":"Set Sample Grading Task","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Read Prompts from Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Limit to Last 10 Prompts","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Gemini Parser Fixer Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Parse Grade Schema","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Candidate Evaluation Agent":{"main":[[{"node":"Grade Evaluation Agent","type":"main","index":0}]]}}}